{"tid":542704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國司機】亂轉線揸車太慢被捕 遊英中國婦怨：都無情講嘅","createTime":"2018-01-27T17:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T18:00:52.000Z","uid":43189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"436b83169659b5c7d88b04a8cc2583cfeb287e67","tid":542704,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517022483_428c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517022483_428c.jpg&h=91725f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名中國女遊客在英國駕車時，行車車速太慢而且胡亂轉線被罰款100英鎊（約1,106港元），因無力付款而被捕。這名女遊客事後抱怨警方做法「殘忍」，又說他們「沒憐憫之心」。<br />\n<br />\n39歲的王喬央（音譯）周三開著租回來的車，前往候城探望朋友，期間被警員截停。控方律師表示，王喬央當時以時速約64公里，在時速113公里的道路上行駛，引起警員關注。律師指：「王喬央在無明確原因下不停轉線，並基於某些原因踏下剎車掣。」王與警員發生爭吵，她說付不起罰款，寧願被捕。<br />\n<br />\n王喬央被鎖監房15小時後出庭，曾留學英國的她，要由普通話傳繹員協助才能作供。王承認未有集中注意力以及不小心駕駛，獲裁判官撤銷控罪。王又說當日警車對她閃燈時，她感到困惑不已，又指警方做法「殘忍」，又說他們「沒憐憫之心」。王獲網開一面後，獨自前往取車離去。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180127/57759571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F57759571&d=rexxOVisv75aJtbrIXBXjV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=d77d4214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F57759571&h=331f253f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180127/57759571</a><br />\n<br />\n有錢租車無錢交罰款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594ec8a094c97d7f6ccf8e1d11365e39b2776c8e","tid":542704,"uid":83582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">曾留學英國的她，要由普通話傳繹員協助才能作供</span><br />\n<br />\n個學歷買返黎?"},{"pid":"c924f4f856270d6b4f979731693ee54b81b12287","tid":542704,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:43:52.000Z","msg":"屌你有錢去英國無錢俾"},{"pid":"78b9c59f2b8a79dc25c77fcd98c44df7500f2ced","tid":542704,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"幫我同佢講聲，情你老母呀！"}]}